1 (h) At the direction of the Commissioner, and in addition to any customary and
2 appropriate audits of the Fund, the governing body of the Fund shall obtain the services of
3 an independent third party designated by the Commissioner on an annual basis to evaluate
4 whether the investments made to the Fund comply with this section.
5 (i) (1) If the Commissioner determines that separate private venture funds
6 are necessary to accomplish the purpose of the Fund, the Commissioner may use money
7 from the Fund to establish additional private venture funds.
8 (2) An additional private venture fund established in accordance with this
9 subsection shall comply with the requirements of subsections (b) through (f) of this section.
